International American Homes Inc said itfiled on May 29 with the Securities and Exchange Commission aregistration statement covering a 25 mln dlr issue ofconvertible subordinated debentures due 2007.    Proceeds will be used to finance the proposed acquisitionof Diversified Shelter Group Ltd and affiliated entities and toretire acquisition indebtedness, International American said.    The company said Moseley Securities Corp would underwritethe offering. Reuter&#3;